.TH "libnvme_ctrl_identify" 9 "libnvme_ctrl_identify" "April 2026" "libnvme API manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
libnvme_ctrl_identify \- Issues an 'identify controller' command
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" libnvme_ctrl_identify
.BI "(libnvme_ctrl_t c "  ","
.BI "struct nvme_id_ctrl *id "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "c" 12
Controller instance
.IP "id" 12
Identify controller data structure
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Issues an 'identify controller' command to \fIc\fP and copies the
data into \fIid\fP.
.SH "RETURN"
0 on success or -1 on failure.
